[SHORT DESC]
Summons permanent sun. 
[LONG DESC]
<p>When this Pokémon is brought out, a permanent sun covers the battlefield. It can only be removed by bringing out a Pokémon with Drizzle or Sand Stream, or by using Rain Dance, Sandstorm, or Hail.</p>

<p>If two Pokemon with weather-changing abilities are sent out at the same time, the weather of the Pokemon with the lower Speed stat will prevail.</p>
<h2>Related Abilities</h2>
<p><a href="/rs/abilities/drizzle">Drizzle</a> is a Rain equivalent.<br />
<a href="/rs/abilities/sand_stream">Sand Stream</a> is a Sandstorm equivalent.</p>